cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with deep learning techniques for traditional image operators, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed decouple learning algorithm involves training two networks jointly, which is a common approach in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of deep networks also suggests the possibility of neural networks (cs.NE) being involved. Finally, the paper deals with image processing, which is a sub-field of multimedia (cs.MM).
